tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: SELECT FUNNEL(${journey.funnel}) FROM usersession where useraction.application in ("${app.name}") ${regionClause1} ${uspClause1}

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select userExperienceScore,count(*) as " " from usersession where useraction.application in ("${app.name}") ${regionClause1} ${uspClause1} and ${journey.where-1} group by userExperienceScore order by count(*) DESC

tiles.name: DTAQL
tiles.query: select count(usersessionid) as " " from usersession where useraction.application in ("${app.name}") ${regionClause1} ${uspClause1} and ${journey.where-1} and not ${journey.where-2}
